# Introduction to Module 0

Before learning **how to use AI**, we must first understand **how software engineering itself has changed**.

Many people believe AI Software Engineering is simply "using ChatGPT to generate code."

That is incorrect.

Generating code is only a tiny part of AI Software Engineering.

Modern AI Software Engineering is a new way of thinking about software development. It changes how products are planned, designed, developed, tested, deployed, monitored, maintained, and improved.

This module establishes the mental framework that will guide every lesson in the course.

