# What Makes This Course Different?

Most AI coding tutorials focus on prompts such as:

> "Ask ChatGPT to build a login page."

While this can be useful, it teaches *tool usage*, not *engineering*.

Our focus is different.

We will learn how to:

* think like an engineer,
* design systems,
* evaluate AI output,
* identify flaws,
* refine implementations,
* and make informed technical decisions.

The objective is to develop engineering judgment alongside AI proficiency.

